definition: appearance/portrait/picture/government minister/(physics) phase/(literary) to appraise (esp. by scrutinizing physical features)/to read sb's fortune (by physiognomy, palmistry etc)
each other/one another/mutually/fret on the neck of a pipa 琵琶[pi2 pa5] (a fret on the soundboard is called a 品[pin3])
as incompatible or irreconcilable as ice and hot coals

sentences.english: And you are saying wait a minute, he has violated the Pauli Exclusion Principle.
sentences.chinese: 你們有人在喊我停一下，說我違反了保利不相容原理。

sentences.english: Religious viewpoints need not conflict with science.
sentences.chinese: 宗教信仰並非一定就與科學水火不相容。

sentences.english: The main objection to animalism is that it conflicts with the psychological-continuity view.
sentences.chinese: 對動物論的主要反對是，這和心理連續觀點不相容。

sentences.english: Both molecules are incompatible with ferric salts.
sentences.chinese: 這兩種分子都與鐵鹽不相容。

sentences.english: The THOG problem is a paradigm to study the exclusive disjunction.
sentences.chinese: THOG問題是研究不相容選言推理的一個實驗範式。

sentences.english: Cultural incompatibility is one of the critical factors which lead to the acquisition failure.
sentences.chinese: 文化的不相容性是導致併購失敗的關鍵因素之一。

sentences.english: This means that the colorant cannot develop its full colour strength in the paint.
sentences.chinese: 有不相容時，色漿在漆中無法完全展色。

sentences.english: Other animals are fundamentally incompatible and do not share any resources.
sentences.chinese: 其他動物基本上是不相容的，並且不共享任何資源。

sentences.english: The participants in irony comprehension build up incompatible mental space by recruiting structures from the same conceptual domains.
sentences.chinese: 從同一概念域話語參與者建立起了不相容的心理空間。

sentences.english: So, the conservation of life right exludes the death penalty.
sentences.chinese: 因此，生命權保護與死刑適用水火不相容也。

sentences.english: A pseudoerosion algorithm is applied to the calculation using the finite difference method, and demonstrated that it is not compatible.
sentences.chinese: 將僞燒蝕算法應用於有限差分的計算，證實其不相容。

sentences.english: Category of system of ownership of the whole people and market economy category are antipathic .
sentences.chinese: 全民所有制範疇與市場經濟範疇是不相容的。

sentences.english: But in China this incompatibility does not exist;
sentences.chinese: 但在中國此不相容性卻不見有。

sentences.english: Its pastor says Islam and Christianity are incompatible.
sentences.chinese: 那個教會的牧師說，伊斯蘭教和基督教是不相容的。

sentences.english: Therefore, Kant's philosophy is incompatible with ecofeminism.
sentences.chinese: 因此，康德哲學與生態女性主義是不相容的。

sentences.english: They might look incompatible at a glance, but they’re not.
sentences.chinese: 它們乍看似乎不相容，但其實不然。
